window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Virtual is reality.</b></p> <p>What would the world be like if video game rules suddenly applied?</p> <p>Marcus is about to find out. After a freak accident, he finds himself stuck between a game and the real world. He’ll need to fight his way through football hooligans, carnies, and the dreaded RNG to get to the final boss and save the world. Anything less means it’s game over for good.</p> <p>Along the way, he’ll learn new skills, chase epic loot, and, most importantly of all, level up!</p> <p>If you love light LitRPG, you'll be sure to enjoy this humorous take on the genre.</p>"; 
